  "detailed_description": "Return to the glory days of sidescrolling beat-em-ups!<br><br>The sinister Milkman holds the city of San Cruces in his nasty criminal grip, and it’s up to legendary black belt neurosurgeon Dr. Karate and the rest of the Fist Puncher team to deliver old-school justice to the lawless streets.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\t19 playable characters<br></li><li>\t50 levels of mayhem<br></li><li>\tPacked with collectibles, Easter Eggs, and secrets<br></li><li>\t99 achievement trading cards to find, plus Steam Trading Cards support<br></li><li>\t2-4 players simultaneous local co-op action<br></li><li>\tAssign “RPG-lite” skill points to level up your crew as you play<br></li><li>\tEach fighter has a unique set of moves and perks to unlock</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Return to the glory days of sidescrolling beat-em-ups!<br><br>The sinister Milkman holds the city of San Cruces in his nasty criminal grip, and it’s up to legendary black belt neurosurgeon Dr. Karate and the rest of the Fist Puncher team to deliver old-school justice to the lawless streets.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\t19 playable characters<br></li><li>\t50 levels of mayhem<br></li><li>\tPacked with collectibles, Easter Eggs, and secrets<br></li><li>\t99 achievement trading cards to find, plus Steam Trading Cards support<br></li><li>\t2-4 players simultaneous local co-op action<br></li><li>\tAssign “RPG-lite” skill points to level up your crew as you play<br></li><li>\tEach fighter has a unique set of moves and perks to unlock</li></ul>",
